name: LIBRA
description: Those born on September 22 - October 22 are Libra zodiac signs. Libra's zodiac sign is the scales and the element of air. Scales represent the side of life that is balanced, orderly, equal, and fair. This is very representative of the Libra person. He knows how to find balance and harmony in life. In any case, Libra will always be a balanced person and do things equally. In addition, Libra is also known as a good adviser.
